text = "Space Battle Tactics

Spawn Controls:
1 - Spawn 3 Fighters (Player)
2 - Spawn 1 Corvette (Player)
3 - Spawn 1 Capital (Player)
4 - Spawn 3 Fighters (Enemy)
5 - Spawn 1 Corvette (Enemy)
6 - Spawn 1 Capital (Enemy)

Camera Controls:
WASD - Pan camera
-/+ - Zoom out/in
/ - Reset camera

After pressing a spawn key, click to place ships."

